title: [Collarly Love]
description: Moonlight fills the small room of stone, cutting through the shadows and bringing cool night air.  A few scarred oak chairs are scattered about, each one topped with colorful cloth cushions.  A placard is attached to a hook on one of the walls.

A cool breeze filters in through the window, bringing much needed freshness to the small room of stone.  A few scarred oak chairs are scattered about, each one topped with colorful cloth cushions.  A placard is attached to a hook on one of the walls.
